Class Question

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.ErpsData
      • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Email
        • de.ityx.mediatrix.data.Question
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    de.ityx.contex.interfaces.white.Licensable, IContent, IEmail, IEmailCompact, IErpsData, IProjectRelation, Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Emaillist

    public class Question
extends Email
implements de.ityx.contex.interfaces.white.Licensable
    The class represents the incoming customer emails and outgoing service center emails. The question is assigned to a case. It's a 1:n relation. The question is assigned only to one case. The case has at least one or more questions except a service center case(@see Case) How to use: for the client call: Question question = new Question(); question.setSubject("test"); question.setCase(caseId); question.setSubprojectId(subprojectId); API.getClientAPI().getQuestionAPI().store(question);
